{"tid":1352141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"笑話一則：香港人罷工","createTime":"2019-07-22T17:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T17:57:41.000Z","uid":139256,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5645e73ec6330838f2f72436850034312b8b9689","tid":1352141,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:38:54.000Z","msg":"先講少少香港罷工史<br />\n<br />\n香港最有名因政治問題而罷工相信係「海員罷工」以及「省港罷工」。 兩次罷工最後都尚算成功，然而呢兩次都已經係遠古歷史。<br />\n<br />\n而就近年叫做有影響力嘅罷力，有「貨櫃碼頭工潮」以及「紮鐵工人罷工」。而民兩次都勉強make到noise。但係一句到尾都係為錢<br />\n<br />\n所以香港人嘅罷工更被唔少政棍取名香港式罷工，好多次都好快收皮。近年嘅罷工都因為利益而成功罷到。你要香港人唔計利益去罷機會好低，因為海員罷工呢件事，背後都會有財主支持先頂到咁耐<br />\n<br />\n然而今次係一個政治性罷工，政治抗爭都係要抗持久，金錢行頭嘅香港人真係理撚你咩。所以勸香港人罷工都哂口水。睇到呢個唔好以後我失敗主義。<br />\n<br />\n[size=6]既然而家係暑假同sem break，一班社會嘅未來棟樑應該幫下香港人，交通係最重要。唔洗覺得唔好意思，失民意。平時個個都話返工辛苦，大家一齊幫下哥哥姐姐，叔叔姨姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297bba9c417ce21d67b6b566777265c0ca92b311","tid":1352141,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:39:08.000Z","msg":"唔好手停口停"},{"pid":"a0be1745fddb9f74e5b095a98b6c9242baf38e30","tid":1352141,"uid":139256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:39:24.000Z","msg":"幫下香港人，地鐵站需要你"},{"pid":"91620fbf06f48a9418387b55dd34d311cb8dc804","tid":1352141,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:40:02.000Z","msg":"推唔切"},{"pid":"fb1095e78ff86ae65e3282f2c1cfd985d6f3cfdc","tid":1352141,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:40:12.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ff010a4ec13d8d087694c5557566cf54479dba58","tid":1352141,"uid":285330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:40:37.000Z","msg":"地鐵不合作運動係唯一贏既方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1343910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1343910</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a87e47de4f752cf70da951419be7428c9c8b3584","tid":1352141,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:41:09.000Z","msg":"大家咁得閒，一於去地鐵站晨運"},{"pid":"b67a0a195e2b11723c1c55f05744745532a954fb","tid":1352141,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:41:28.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"7e8fca3a4408bf5d78cf8bc4b67d6b13aca7b561","tid":1352141,"uid":139256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:43:33.000Z","msg":"香港年輕人站起來喇，反正做咩都俾人話廢青"},{"pid":"46d98a779bab847512414e44a9827e40fd45513e","tid":1352141,"uid":139256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:45:10.000Z","msg":"反正大家都係排下喜茶，路過地鐵站咪幫下人囉"},{"pid":"af349d9b777be37d62ce2f653c233025f853ba12","tid":1352141,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:46:16.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"4eb14fe0cbd9cf7dc31ee5c62c3a3029081a5d6f","tid":1352141,"uid":100892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:46:51.000Z","msg":"叫香港僱主罷工真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"924772a114a8689bb3fca5f86891ddf9e9d8f596","tid":1352141,"uid":139256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:47:34.000Z","msg":"講真嘅勸佢地罷，不如直接出手幫佢地"},{"pid":"f4500dbe312f20d59a993c9b2ad37a6988aae280","tid":1352141,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:48:51.000Z","msg":"學識歷史嘅教訓喇，無利益衝突真係睬你都有味"},{"pid":"e8e0ace3b0fe253cb224b19e4c8c81c851733854","tid":1352141,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:51:06.000Z","msg":"Btw毋忘69到而家嘅一切，由612濫用暴力到上環同警黑合作。呢段時間無勝利過"},{"pid":"46b60dfaedc4d0d3d55ec7123d017b6e49b292b9","tid":1352141,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:52:01.000Z","msg":"推呀，大學生，中學生"},{"pid":"7042b982353cd15ff2f27722b8f8f0ff6aa3bb91","tid":1352141,"uid":139256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:53:48.000Z","msg":"三罷係可以有個好美好嘅結果<br />\n但你覺得勸到香港人咩"},{"pid":"1c8985ac82fe485c011f8310d2ce7861cb0fc75e","tid":1352